);\n    z-index: -1;\n}\n\n\/* Chevron with background *\/\n.dynamic-button::after {\n    content: '\u203a';\n    position: absolute;\n    right: 20px;\n    top: 50%;\n    transform: translateY(-50%) scale(0);\n    background-color: #2D2D2D;\n    color: white;\n    width: 30px;\n    height: 30px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);\n    opacity: 0;\n}\n\n\/* Hover effects *\/\n.dynamic-button:hover {\n    color: #2D2D2D;\n    padding-right: 70px;\n}\n\n.dynamic-button:hover::before {\n    transform: scale(0);\n}\n\n.dynamic-button:hover::after {\n    transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1);\n    opacity: 1;\n}\n<\/style>\n\n<a href=\"https:\/\/wa.me\/919953879928?text=Hi%20I%20want%20to%20book%20a%201-1%20session%20with%20you\" class=\"dynamic-button\">Book a free 1:1 consultation<\/a>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c455fbd e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c455fbd\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c6821ae e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"c6821ae\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c668df8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c668df8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><b>This space<\/b> is <\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9718192 elementor-headline--style-highlight elementor-widget elementor-widget-animated-headline\" data-id=\"9718192\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;marker&quot;:&quot;underline_zigzag&quot;,&quot;highlighted_text&quot;:&quot;for you&quot;,&quot;highlight_animation_duration&quot;:0,&quot;headline_style&quot;:&quot;highlight&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"animated-headline.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-headline\">\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-headline-dynamic-wrapper elementor-headline-text-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-headline-dynamic-text elementor-headline-text-active\">for you<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3686d62 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3686d62\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ea057ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ea057ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"443\" height=\"470\" src=\"https:\/\/okutherapy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Frame-243.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-678\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/okutherapy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Frame-243.png 443w, https:\/\/okutherapy.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/Frame-243-283x300.png 283w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 443px) 100vw, 443px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3103af7 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3103af7\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3e89634 elementor-widget__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3e89634\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>We\u2019re not meant to heal in isolation. You\u2019re not the only one who struggles to ask for help\u2014who wonders if others feel this lonely, this pained, who longs to belong but fears being seen.<\/p><p>At Oku, we believe something quietly transformative happens when we come together\u2014when the burden of being \u201cthe only one\u201d begins to dissolve.<\/p><p>Our group spaces are warm, non-performative, and deeply human. They\u2019re here for the days when you need more than words\u2014and for the days when words come more easily in the company of others.<\/p><p>This is Oku | People. <br \/>A gentle reminder that you don\u2019t have to do this alone.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-994aece elementor-widget__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"994aece\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In our group spaces, you\u2019ll find:<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e406ab1 elementor-hidden-desktop elementor-hidden-tablet elementor-hidden-mobile elementor-widget elementor-widget-html\" data-id=\"e406ab1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"html.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<script>\n    \n    \/\/ JavaScript code\ndocument.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n    \/\/ Check if device is not mobile\n    function isNotMobile() {\n        return window.innerWidth > 768;\n    }\n    \n    const summaContainers = document.querySelectorAll('.summa');\n    \n    summaContainers.forEach(container => {\n        container.addEventListener('mouseenter', function() {\n            \/\/ Only apply hover effect on non-mobile devices\n            if (isNotMobile()) {\n                \/\/ Remove active class from all summa containers\n                summaContainers.forEach(c => c.classList.remove('active'));\n                \n                \/\/ Add active class to the hovered container\n                this.classList.add('active');\n            }\n        });\n    });\n});\n    \n<\/script>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4a02ba0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4a02ba0\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ea9b3dc e-con-full summa active e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"ea9b3dc\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7ccafee e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"7ccafee\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8ccea23 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"8ccea23\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0f9ec9f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0f9ec9f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Support Groups<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-83832c0 poda elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"83832c0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>For trauma survivors, queer individuals, chronically ill folks, and those navigating loss, loneliness, change, or addictions.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\